GIVING AWAY BUBBLE MILK TEA!!!
Launching our very first giveaway for @ShersChoice to celebrate Mother’s Day! All you have to do is to comment below a brown sugar recipe you would like to create for your mum!! It can be sweet or savory, be creative~ We will be choosing 2 participants’ recipes to win this set of bubble tea + 1 packet of our original brown sugar! To qualify :
— 1. Follow @Shermainexk & @ShersChoice
2. Comment below what brown sugar creation you’ll like to prepare for your mum 💕 4. 2 participants will walk away with a pack of 5 DIY Taiwanese bubble tea + 1 pack of our original brown sugar! #ShersChoice #GiveawaysWithSher

My mom loves garlic and brown sugar, so I’d love to prepare honey garlic brown sugar chicken for her! 🍗😋 This involves seasoning chicken thighs with salt and pepper. Add unsalted butter to the skillet on medium fire, then put the chicken in and sear. Remove the chicken. Add more butter and garlic into the skillet and mix - once you can smell the aroma, remove from heat and pour in brown sugar, honey, dried basil and thyme. Drench the mixture over the chicken and roast ‘em in the oven. Hoping to achieve a beautiful brown sweet garlicky glaze 😍
